"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"When investing, leverage can be a powerful tool.  \\n\\nExample: Buy a $400,000 house, but you only need $80,000 (20% down payment) or $14,000 (3.5% FHA loan) if you’re going to live there.\\n\\nNow, you control an asset worth $400,000 instead of $80,000 or $14,000.\\n\\nWhen that asset appreciates 5% in year one, that’s 5% of $400,000 (which is $20,000) vs. 5% of $14,000 (which is only $700).  That’s over 28x the results.\\n\\nNow, you might argue that you’ve taken on debt which is bad.  You HAVE taken on debt, but if it’s at today’s current interest rates (around 3-4%), this is actually amazing debt.  The posted CPI numbers at the time of this writing are over 6%, so you’re actually borrowing the money at less than inflation.\\n\\nThis means you’re getting PAID to borrow the money.\\n\\nLeverage and debt can be amazing wealth creators if you understand some basic principles.\",\"timestamp\":1638671652,\"title\":\"2 Amazing Wealth Builders: Leverage & Debt\"},\"digest\":\"-20Wqk6mJ_mfNKLKXNQmoRuHHlrtF2NLrzmJXQuPs2w\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAC3C2b498A9f44b237ed5946e21Ba14676A54211\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c_lXRDUlYieB08uKRusIu0aAD47NurKzo6YKn5HkqHM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tfnFr_FPMdil0-AlDXdzEPPvI9CWfLGnUXDjCJGz0Wc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yIOxD-SZg2DFZ2oo7K_PkESgBf105LGXYLbR1QbHRADF5T-vONosbNdd_Ep7CCO7LGvreYOb1XgSMhwpIntFHQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x19ac6167229d8850d767328fb6ed4ca854dc1511cf75f01e943de2bad10bf3b57b62e7b56125076358a7bc87425bc161b0c3724ab43d0ef583dda7c5cc92dbf31b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c_lXRDUlYieB08uKRusIu0aAD47NurKzo6YKn5HkqHM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tfnFr_FPMdil0-AlDXdzEPPvI9CWfLGnUXDjCJGz0Wc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"h